== Posting Links for New Users ==
To prevent spam, posting hyperlinks in {{project_name_long}} forums is disabled for new users. An alternative is to use code tags for links; instead of just writing the link, surround it by prepending and appending an apostrophe ("<code>`</code>"). Example:

{{CodeSelect|code=
`https://www.{{project_clearnet}}`
}}

Or make a new line for a link and add 4 white spaces in front of it. Example:

<pre>
    https://www.kicksecure.com
</pre>

New users accounts that do not post spam are eventually permitted to post links.

