== Pasting Logs for Support ==
It is acceptable to paste logs to {{project_name_long}} forums, even lengthy ones.

Sometimes the forum software does not permit the posting of lengthy logs. In this case, split the log into multiple posts if reasonable or consider using a free pastebin service instead such as [https://notes.anonpaste.org/ AnonPaste] or [https://privatebin.net/ PrivateBin]. Afterwards, copy the link to the pasted log in your forum post.

